Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:39.16,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Pesci! \NWhat the fuck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.91,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Pesci!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.79,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Stop the damn train already!{Hurry up and stop the train!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.46,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Pesci!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.84,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,B-Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.67,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Stop the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.51,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.52,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I-I dunno how to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.23,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,This will put an end \Nto you and your aging ability.{OLD: Now you and your aging ability will be done for.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:07.32,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Then my crew will return to normal, \N and Trish will be safe! {shounen af}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.65,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.86,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.53,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.58,Thoughts,Bruno,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:23.33,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Prosciutto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.00,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,W-Well done, Pesci!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.96,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Excellent work! \N That was quick thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.01,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,A-Almost lost him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.30,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I almost missed my chance... \N Thank goodness I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.01,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,My hook will never let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:44.69,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,B-But this resistance I feel \N is the weight of two people! {Do we want a more liberal take? 手応え can mean resistance, but I think in this situation it's less "resistance" and more haptic, i.e. "tugging on the line" when taken along with 重さ. See Jisho for definitions of 手応え. Also, "resistance" doesn't feel very Pesci to me. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:48.31,Thoughts,Pesci,0,0,0,,Buccellati's gotta be hanging on, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:56.03,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I seriously thought you'd \Nfucked me for good, Buccellati. {おしまい - we really want to get across that Prosciutto thought it was curtains for him, see? NYAH, so I added in "for good", see? NYAH -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:01.29,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I called you a failure of a capo, \N but I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.41,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have been so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.92,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're the kind of guy who knows \N how to make tough decisions in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.71,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Even when your life is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:16.80,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,The boss was wise to pick you \N to protect his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.64,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I'm seriously shocked. {minor, but... he いやs here, yet I'm not sure if it matters in this particular instance. major: I think he's really saying that he's impressed, less so shocked that the boss selected him as Trish's guardian. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.27,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Even so, Buccellati...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:24.64,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're one hell of an unlucky capo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:30.94,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Down you go!{OLD: Now fall!} \N A 150-kilometer-an-hour trip to hell awaits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sticky Fingers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.94,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.24,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're still aging as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.12,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:47.87,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The line your younger brother \N sent out for you really saved me. {For BDs: Is "younger bro" really good for Bruno? Even if he heard Pesci throwing out "aniki"s left and right like a 1980s yanki, I'd suggest changing this line to "your teammate" or "your companion" or something along those lines -Gyro}{yeah, I don't like it either, really. He does outright say 弟, which is younger ("little" brother). -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.17,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,He wasn't aiming for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.34,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Am I the unlucky one here? {Ugh, I so want to make this "Am *I* the one who's out of luck?" but this is clearly a callback to line 34 (lol 34) and it's not easy to work in "out of luck" when he also says "kanbu", aka capo, in said line. -Starfish}{seconded, but alas. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:58.55,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,There's no way \Nthat asshole Mista {OLD: should have}survived earlier! {This is maybe a bit too far removed, though the sentiment's right. Sun-Dried Ham here is actually saying that it's plain fucked up that asshole Mista was somehow still alive (which I now see that this feeds into what he says two lines later). Thoughts on how to wrangle this? -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.18,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I put three bullets right through his skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:09.77,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,The fact that he's alive is more fucked up \N than someone saying the sun rises in the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.73,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,I told him how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.15,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Any energy that hits the fishing line...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.99,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,...gets sent back to whoever's hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.82,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.62,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.67,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,It's one person lighter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:33.04,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Buccellati musta been thrown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:36.01,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,We did it, Prosciutto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.59,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Looks like his aging ability's been cancelled. {OLD: stopped working. 解除される can probably be stretched to mean this, but the JP term used is fairly strong, like "fucking donezo". -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.93,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Now we just gotta deal with \N the fishing line dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.06,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:56.86,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Earlier, my Beach Boy's hook \N shoulda dug into Bro's right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.16,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,His pinky was on the right side of the hook...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.16,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:11.54,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,...there's a pinky on the left side...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.38,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,It's attached to a left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.34,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:20.68,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Whose hand {\i1}is{\i0} that on the other end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:25.18,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,How'd it switch from \N Bro's right hand to his left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:31.02,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,N-Now that I think about it... \N Bro was a bit heavier'n this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.02,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}H-Hey, you over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:35.65,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Make them stop the train! \N I think everyone here is sick or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:39.49,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I feel better than I did \Njust a minute ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:42.36,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}I lost a bunch of teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:42.36,Thoughts,Pesci,0,0,0,,Th-The effects of his aging are reversing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.03,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.24,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Go get the driver to stop the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.58,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:52.46,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the weight \N that fell off the line was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.54,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.50,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,It can't be! \N It can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.63,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,B-Bro can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.26,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me, you clown?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.59,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you! \N {\i1}You,{\i0} right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.47,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,My bro, Prosciutto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.85,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,What should I do? \N What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.93,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:14.40,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Oh, no! \N The guys inside the tortoise are gonna come out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.44,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wh-What should I do? \N What should I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.44,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}What the hell are you crying over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.32,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I told you to stop the damn train!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.15,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up, {\i1}shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.11,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.11,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}You some kind of mammone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.41,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fine! I'm starting to feel better anyway, \N so I'll just tell them my{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.46,Thoughts,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.34,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop... the... train...{This wasn't in the CR subs but I'm clearly hearing "to... me... te..." here. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.88,Thoughts,Pesci,0,0,0,,The aging hasn't stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.13,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Buccellati, y-you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.47,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.05,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... \N Don't tell me he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.52,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:59.48,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Grateful... Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.65,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:12.91,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,You were right, Bro... \N You were so right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:17.71,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,You told me that I should never call back my Stand \N once I'm close to defeating the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:22.84,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,...even if it means losing an arm or leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.88,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,B-Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:30.05,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way he's gonna make it \Nwith how messed up he is...{OLD: With those awful, fatal injuries, \N th-there's no way he'll live...}{I went super liberal here -- Pesci does mention "serious injuries" (重傷), but we missed the mark on グチャグチャ. "Fatal" is kind of too far, even with "guchagucha" (pulpy) modifying "serious injuries". -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.14,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,It won't be long before he stops breathing...{The phrasing used in Japanese literally translates to "retires his breathing". So we might want to have some sort of slang here too to reflect that... Just as long as it's not too silly. I briefly considered "buys the farm" here but... yeah no. -Starfish}{Tried to think of a unique way to word this, but I couldn't think of anything that felt right -T}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:38.48,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,...yet Bro still isn't releasing Grateful Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:48.61,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,We've gotta get Trish, no matter what. \N Right, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.62,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,We can't turn back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.50,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I get it now, Prosciutto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.96,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Your resolve...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:05.30,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I understand what you meant \N not just in words, but also deep within my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.51,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Once our mind's made up\N to {\i1}get{\i0} someone... {TLC-san made a note to keep this continuous w/ lines 137-138 in GW 15. Repeating that note here. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:13.22,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,...the deed's already been done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:28.74,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,That's the first time I offed someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:32.53,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wasn't as big of a deal as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:41.54,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,And now that this guy's gone, \N there's no one left to call me a mammone.
Comment: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.85,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I'm gonna finish this once and for all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.72,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,...before Bro's ability disappears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:59.89,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Buccellati! \N Hurry up and take the hook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.90,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Got it.
