Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:37.01,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm sure they told the others about \N the tortoise and where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.97,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,We'll have to find \N a different mode of transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.77,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,I've been meaning \N to ask you something... {did you ever get me my water? does this make me look fat? why is the sky blue?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.43,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Will you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.94,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I haven't been given permission \N to answer any of your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.94,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Our sole mission is to act as your bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.28,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.78,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Just {\i1}who{\i0} am I? {here she's very heavily implying that she's changed somehow, right before she explicitly states her symptoms. Literally having a freakout at possibly being something other than human... it's more like "who or what" for 何者. Leave it up to you guys to determine what's appropriate here. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.99,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}this{\i0} supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.53,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,What's this on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:07.37,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Why have I suddenly started \N seeing such bizarre things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:13.25,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Why am I being pursued \N over a father I've never even met?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:17.63,Thoughts,Bruno,0,0,0,,I knew it... \N The boss's daughter is a Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.47,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Comment: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.27,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,The current time is 6:34 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:34.11,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I arrived twenty minutes \N after the train stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.03,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Prosciutto is lying dead near the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:41.40,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Dismembered pieces of Pesci's body \N are strewn across the riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:46.79,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Judging from the state of things, I can conclude that \N Buccellati's Sticky Fingers was responsible for eliminating them. {whoof... guessing there's no real good way to split this without paying a CPS/frame snapping tax? -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.45,Narrator,Ghiaccio?,0,0,0,,Got it. \N What about his team and the girl? {OLD: Got it. Where are his team and the girl?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.54,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.29,Narrator,Ghiaccio?,0,0,0,,Can you track them down, Melone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.25,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:59.34,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,The measures taken by the now-deceased \N should make tracking them possible. {maybe recently deceased instead? now-deceased (an adjective) is weird without a noun to modify. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.39,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,I just procured a blood sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.39,Main,Melone,0,0,0,,Buccellati's, as it were. {I CAN TELL BECAUSE I GOT SPECIAL EYES}
